{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/information-technology/line-notify","result":{"data":{"blogImage":{"edges":[]},"oldBlogImage":{"edges":[{"node":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/5f035/LINE.png","srcSet":"/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/1f8a1/LINE.png 80w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/e9a79/LINE.png 160w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/5f035/LINE.png 320w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/eadd3/LINE.png 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 320px) 320px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/793cf/LINE.avif 80w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/6de5b/LINE.avif 160w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/20389/LINE.avif 320w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/8c32c/LINE.avif 640w","type":"image/avif","sizes":"(min-width: 320px) 320px, 100vw"},{"srcSet":"/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/61ca6/LINE.webp 80w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/60b4d/LINE.webp 160w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/5e011/LINE.webp 320w,\n/static/dbfd2467601761e5c14ebf1a093a1061/90d07/LINE.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 320px) 320px, 100vw"}]},"width":320,"height":320}}}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"22180917-0785-55d2-8664-32957ab5bb49","excerpt":"概要 コミュニケーションツールとして、多くの方のスマートフォンに導入されているであろうLINE。それに自動的に通知を送れる仕組みがあれば便利と思い作成したので公開します。 できること リマインダーのように特定の日時に通知を送る。 特定の曜日に通知を送る。 第…","html":"<h2>概要</h2>\n<p>コミュニケーションツールとして、多くの方のスマートフォンに導入されているであろうLINE。それに自動的に通知を送れる仕組みがあれば便利と思い作成したので公開します。</p>\n<h3>できること</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>リマインダーのように特定の日時に通知を送る。</li>\n<li>特定の曜日に通知を送る。</li>\n<li>第3水曜日だけに～といったことも可能。</li>\n<li>毎日繰り返し通知する。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>必要なもの</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>LINEアカウント（Web上でメールアドレスログインできること）</li>\n<li>Googleアカウント</li>\n</ul>\n<p>そして、無料です。LINEやGoogleが提供してくれているサービスに感謝です。</p>\n<h2>手順</h2>\n<h3>通知定義スプレッドシートをコピー</h3>\n<p>下記のスプレッドシートをご自身のGoogleDriveに<strong>コピー</strong>してください。【注意】<strong>必ずコピー</strong>をしてください。編集リクエストをするのでは<strong>ありません</strong>。よく間違えて編集リクエストを送ってくる方がいますのでご注意ください。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qwfqN2qZUugmTM7jOw-Rp0TDBpcgZ2MHR9PmLaVoSFo/edit?usp=sharing\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1qwfqN2qZUugmTM7jOw-Rp0TDBpcgZ2MHR9PmLaVoSFo/edit?usp=sharing</a></p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/abbfe/image-6-1024x487.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/85704/image-6-1024x487.webp 240w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/2d484/image-6-1024x487.webp 480w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/ac99e/image-6-1024x487.webp 960w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/d757a/image-6-1024x487.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/74bfa/image-6-1024x487.png 240w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/b3a52/image-6-1024x487.png 480w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/97137/image-6-1024x487.png 960w,\n/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/abbfe/image-6-1024x487.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/82f4bc3992fae501854a245fddef69d6/97137/image-6-1024x487.png\"\n            alt=\"image 6 1024x487\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>ファイル＞コピーを作成を選んで、自分のGoogleDriveにコピーしてください。<br>\n（Googleにログインしている必要があります。）</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 522px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/e66f6/image-7.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 85.83333333333334%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/85704/image-7.webp 240w,\n/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/2d484/image-7.webp 480w,\n/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/b5e96/image-7.webp 522w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 522px) 100vw, 522px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/74bfa/image-7.png 240w,\n/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/b3a52/image-7.png 480w,\n/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/e66f6/image-7.png 522w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 522px) 100vw, 522px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7de616f2b38fc811bb086db3e17a3e4e/e66f6/image-7.png\"\n            alt=\"image 7\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>名前やフォルダの場所はどこでも良いです。（後でも変えられます。）</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h3>通知定義を編集</h3>\n<p>いくつかサンプルを載せています。これらを参考に贈りたい通知を記載してください。（まだ通知されないのでご安心を）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/abbfe/image-8-1024x340.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 33.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/85704/image-8-1024x340.webp 240w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/2d484/image-8-1024x340.webp 480w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/ac99e/image-8-1024x340.webp 960w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/d757a/image-8-1024x340.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/74bfa/image-8-1024x340.png 240w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/b3a52/image-8-1024x340.png 480w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/97137/image-8-1024x340.png 960w,\n/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/abbfe/image-8-1024x340.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/12c8781a7f0fe5455b399458b8dd2875/97137/image-8-1024x340.png\"\n            alt=\"image 8 1024x340\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>説明：<br>\n①「通知有効」列の✔を外せば通知されません。<br>\n②「メッセージ」に記載した内容がLINEに通知されます。（必須）<br>\n③「時刻」に通知を送りたい時刻を記載してください。（必須）<br>\n④「特定日付」特定の日に通知したい場合は記載してください。リマインダーとして使えます。<br>\n⑤「曜日」特定の曜日に通知したい場合は、該当の曜日に✔をつけてください。<br>\n⑥「第○曜日」例えば、第3水曜日のみに通知を送りたい場合は、「3」を記載して水曜日に✔をつければ良いです。「2,4」などとカンマ区切りで複数指定もできます。</p>\n<h3>LINEの通知botを作る</h3>\n<p>下記LINEの開発者サイトにアクセスしてLINEのアカウントでログインします。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://notify-bot.line.me/ja/\">https://notify-bot.line.me/ja/</a></p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/abbfe/image-2-1024x417.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/85704/image-2-1024x417.webp 240w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/2d484/image-2-1024x417.webp 480w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/ac99e/image-2-1024x417.webp 960w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/d757a/image-2-1024x417.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/74bfa/image-2-1024x417.png 240w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/b3a52/image-2-1024x417.png 480w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/97137/image-2-1024x417.png 960w,\n/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/abbfe/image-2-1024x417.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/738c739da280c507e8d71c5e69508522/97137/image-2-1024x417.png\"\n            alt=\"image 2 1024x417\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>右上の「ログイン」を押して、LINEのメールアドレスとパスワードでログインしてください。</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/e61f0/image-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.416666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/85704/image-3.webp 240w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/2d484/image-3.webp 480w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/ac99e/image-3.webp 960w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/b4431/image-3.webp 983w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/74bfa/image-3.png 240w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/b3a52/image-3.png 480w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/97137/image-3.png 960w,\n/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/e61f0/image-3.png 983w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/15406abe4a74abc090988a7104f509d6/97137/image-3.png\"\n            alt=\"image 3\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>「トークンを発行する」を押します。</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 585px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/0cdfa/image-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 145.41666666666669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/85704/image-4.webp 240w,\n/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/2d484/image-4.webp 480w,\n/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/724ac/image-4.webp 585w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/74bfa/image-4.png 240w,\n/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/b3a52/image-4.png 480w,\n/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/0cdfa/image-4.png 585w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 585px) 100vw, 585px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9764e11d9ac6910b0015235a67d36553/0cdfa/image-4.png\"\n            alt=\"image 4\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>①トークン名を入力してください。<br>\nここで設定したものが（仮にXXとすると）、「[XX]通知メッセージ～」といった形で通知されます。<br>\n②通知するトークルームを選択してください。<br>\nそのルームに対して通知されるようになります。ここで「1:1でLINE Notifyから通知を受け取る」を選ぶと自分だけに通知されます。<br>\n③「発行する」ボタンを押してください。</p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 583px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/8e474/image-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 82.91666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/85704/image-5.webp 240w,\n/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/2d484/image-5.webp 480w,\n/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/ba431/image-5.webp 583w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/74bfa/image-5.png 240w,\n/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/b3a52/image-5.png 480w,\n/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/8e474/image-5.png 583w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 583px) 100vw, 583px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c59cf1c982c1dfcabc426bcdb2cce08e/8e474/image-5.png\"\n            alt=\"image 5\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>ランダムなトークンが発行されるので、コピーしてください。</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h3>通知機能を動かす</h3>\n<p>スプレッドシートの「設定」シートを開いてください。そのB2セルにさきほどLINEで発行したトークンを貼り付けます。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/abbfe/image-9-1024x487.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/85704/image-9-1024x487.webp 240w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/2d484/image-9-1024x487.webp 480w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/ac99e/image-9-1024x487.webp 960w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/d757a/image-9-1024x487.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/74bfa/image-9-1024x487.png 240w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/b3a52/image-9-1024x487.png 480w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/97137/image-9-1024x487.png 960w,\n/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/abbfe/image-9-1024x487.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c0597973953e57af309a481a0f0ef2a7/97137/image-9-1024x487.png\"\n            alt=\"image 9 1024x487\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>そして、ツール＞スクリプトエディタをクリックします。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/abbfe/image-10-1024x487.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/85704/image-10-1024x487.webp 240w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/2d484/image-10-1024x487.webp 480w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/ac99e/image-10-1024x487.webp 960w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/d757a/image-10-1024x487.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/74bfa/image-10-1024x487.png 240w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/b3a52/image-10-1024x487.png 480w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/97137/image-10-1024x487.png 960w,\n/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/abbfe/image-10-1024x487.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/9d54acd0e2bce799b224d4526134d173/97137/image-10-1024x487.png\"\n            alt=\"image 10 1024x487\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>すると、こんな画面が出てきますので、以下の時計のようなアイコンをクリックします。（ちなみに、ここにLINEに通知するプログラムが書かれています。）</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/abbfe/image-12-1024x487.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/85704/image-12-1024x487.webp 240w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/2d484/image-12-1024x487.webp 480w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/ac99e/image-12-1024x487.webp 960w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/d757a/image-12-1024x487.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/74bfa/image-12-1024x487.png 240w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/b3a52/image-12-1024x487.png 480w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/97137/image-12-1024x487.png 960w,\n/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/abbfe/image-12-1024x487.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c58da96eb714ffb80e7cba7ae25b3824/97137/image-12-1024x487.png\"\n            alt=\"image 12 1024x487\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>トリガー画面になるので、「トリガーを追加」ボタンを押します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 960px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/abbfe/image-13-1024x487.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/85704/image-13-1024x487.webp 240w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/2d484/image-13-1024x487.webp 480w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/ac99e/image-13-1024x487.webp 960w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/d757a/image-13-1024x487.webp 1024w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/74bfa/image-13-1024x487.png 240w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/b3a52/image-13-1024x487.png 480w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/97137/image-13-1024x487.png 960w,\n/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/abbfe/image-13-1024x487.png 1024w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/caf4bc4535758feca2442072c7239735/97137/image-13-1024x487.png\"\n            alt=\"image 13 1024x487\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>そうしたら、下記の通りに設定して、「保存」ボタンを押します。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 702px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/02128/image-14.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 113.75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/85704/image-14.webp 240w,\n/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/2d484/image-14.webp 480w,\n/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/0bc03/image-14.webp 702w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/74bfa/image-14.png 240w,\n/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/b3a52/image-14.png 480w,\n/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/02128/image-14.png 702w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/aecdc9a6ca016fd487c125aa315ef85a/02128/image-14.png\"\n            alt=\"image 14\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>実行する関数を選択：　main</li>\n<li>実行するデプロイを選択：　HEAD</li>\n<li>イベントのソースを選択：　時間主導型</li>\n<li>時間ベースのトリガーのタイプを選択：　分ベースのタイマー</li>\n<li>時間の間隔を選択（分）：　1分おき</li>\n<li>エラー通知設定：　（何でもよいです）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>設定完了</h3>\n<p>以上で設定完了です。時間になったら通知が飛ぶようになっています。</p>\n<figure>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 437px; margin-left: initial;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/96f1a/image-15.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 20%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/85704/image-15.webp 240w,\n/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/5a20f/image-15.webp 437w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/74bfa/image-15.png 240w,\n/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/96f1a/image-15.png 437w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5cadefecf8c6a31f6c0f0bd5015c4a76/96f1a/image-15.png\"\n            alt=\"image 15\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<figcaption>\n<p>こんな感じで通知が飛びます。</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2>参考情報（開発者向け）</h2>\n<p>ソースコードは下記で管理しています。<br>\nType Script で書いており、Google謹製の <a href=\"https://github.com/google/clasp\">clasp</a> というツールで管理しています。clasp はDockerで動かせるようにしているので、ローカル環境を汚しません。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/nisioka/line%5C_notify\">https://github.com/nisioka/line\\_notify</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/line-notify/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"3分で出来る LINEへの自動定期通知システム簡単構築","date":"2020/06/18","dateModified":null,"description":null,"category":null,"categories":["information-technology","life"],"tags":["clasp","google-app-scripts","spreadsheet"]}},"mdPrevious":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/labs-play-with-k8s-com/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"ブラウザで簡単にkubernatesで遊ぼう（labs.play-with-k8s.com）","category":null,"categories":["information-technology"]}},"mdNext":{"fields":{"slug":"/posts/login-for-novice/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"認証処理の心得【初心者向け】","category":null,"categories":["information-technology"]}}},"pageContext":{"id":"22180917-0785-55d2-8664-32957ab5bb49","previousPostId":"6eb63b89-205b-5639-8fbd-9bf3662282a3","nextPostId":"5114ae26-b81